{"lastModified":1765790453876,"uri":"c::7819217464::vessel::490fd9f0-cc11-11ee-bf8a-ad14a1404930","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey\n\nRefitted in 2021, HAPPY DAYS is a spacious motor-sailer with a classic exterior look and modern interior. 10 guests can comfortably be accommodated in 5 cabins which include 2 masters, 1 double and 2 twins. The aft master with its’ panoramic sea view is particularly romantic. All cabins are en-suite and with 24 hour air-conditioning. The aft deck hosts full beam wide lounging cushions, a dining table that can easily seat 10 guests and a fully stocked bar for speedy service. A soft top cover that can be folded down to deck level offers protection from wind and sun when required. On the forward deck there is ample space with sunbathing mattresses for all guests and a seating area with two sunset cocktail tables. HAPPY DAYS comes with a 6.80m tender with a 200hp outboard engine, far more powerful compared to other vessels of her size, allowing for fantastic water sport experience. A professional crew of 5 are onboard to offer service with famous Turkish hospitality for an unforgettable vacation.","blueprint":{"name":"HAPPY DAYS","images":["/media/media::image::c::7819217464::vessel::490fd9f0-cc11-11ee-bf8a-ad14a1404930::assets::7844eb21-bcc0-11ef-881f-f57cb0c05129/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819217464::vessel::490fd9f0-cc11-11ee-bf8a-ad14a1404930::assets::784b05a0-bcc0-11ef-8820-f57cb0c05129/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819217464::vessel::490fd9f0-cc11-11ee-bf8a-ad14a1404930::assets::7813f010-bcc0-11ef-881f-f57cb0c05129/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819217464::vessel::490fd9f0-cc11-11ee-bf8a-ad14a1404930::assets::78456050-bcc0-11ef-881f-f57cb0c05129/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819217464::vessel::490fd9f0-cc11-11ee-bf8a-ad14a1404930::assets::78519550-bcc0-11ef-8821-f57cb0c05129/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819217464::vessel::490fd9f0-cc1